   <talk_paragraph index="n1629_smith-1-a" image="QN_Npc_roffie_ghost.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1629_smith-1-b" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah, he was a victim too.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Pirate Smith$<BR>So the captain's soul was separated from his body too? That's why he was talking nonsense in Saint Haven...?<BR>Then he wasn't pretending to be crazy for being the only survivor...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1629_smith-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1629_smith-1-c" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I didn't see it either.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Pirate Smith$<BR>I went in there to see if my body was there.<BR>But I couldn't stay for long and I didn't see my body anywhere.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1629_smith-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1629_smith-1-d" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Pirate Smith$<BR>And I keep seeing Monolith in my dream... in my dream my body and soul are separated and the soul enters a gnoll's body, and my body is sucked into the other side of the Monolith... Is my body on the other side of the Monolith's door?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1629_smith-1-d" image="QN_Npc_lifius.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1629_smith-1-e" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you have a plan?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Pirate Smith$<BR>That means Lipius who opened the door or the captain needs to come back to their senses first... I've made up my mind! I'm going to get my body back!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1629_smith-1-e" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400445" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
