      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Pirate Smith$<BR>I can't stay there for long. I could enter only because the Monolith separated my body from my soul. But I still felt sick after being there for a few minutes! Please help me get the pirate items!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Go to the Eye of the Goddess)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
